    BoundedDateInput, BoundedInput<java.util.Date>, HTML5Input, Input<java.util.Date>, ParseInput<java.util.Date>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DayMultiInput, MonthMultiInput

    public class TimeStampMultiInput
extends AbstractCalendarMultiInput
implements BoundedDateInput
    An input that selects a timestamp using pull down menus. The class also implements ParseInput to support setting default values.

    various time fields can be suppressed by passing a Calendar field value to the constructor. Only those fields greater or equal to this value are shown. The year value is always shown.

    Values for the suppressed fields will be remembered by the input though not editable by the UI.
